Hunger and malnutrition are among the biggest challenges facing humanity, claiming a child’s life every 10 seconds.
The 100 Million Meals’ campaign represents the Emirates contribution to global efforts to combat hunger and malnutrition as part of the SDGs Goal to end hunger by 2030. 

Each one of us can make a difference and donate. Together we can end hunger.  Donate to - 
https://www.100millionmeals.ae
